    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay so u said they work in the short term but then say they cause instability. if they cause instability and target specific groups, does that mean they're actually a failed policy overall? like, is there even a real argument for them anymore or are they just outdated?",
      "source": "evaluator"
